  04 Jun 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org>
  lxqt-meta-0.9.0-r2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Move various kde-base packages to kde-apps.

  15 Apr 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> lxqt-meta-0.9.0-r2.ebuild:
  keyword arm/arm64, tested on cortex-A9/A53 hardware; support lxqt, bug 528676

*lxqt-meta-0.9.0-r2 (15 Mar 2015)

  15 Mar 2015; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org> +lxqt-meta-0.9.0-r2.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Add dependencies for oxygen-icons (bug #528676) and virtual/ttf-fonts, as they
  are expected in the default install.

